data.description: Single-story house offering cost-saving benefits with owned solar panels. Features include 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an open floor plan with abundant natural light. The spacious living room boasts a charming fireplace connected to a spacious kitchen with an island, a bar area, and a great pantry. Additionally, there is a delightful dining nook with lovely windows in the kitchen. The master bedroom is generously sized and includes a bathroom suite with dual sinks, a soaking tub, and a large walk-in closet. Two more spacious bedrooms and another bathroom complete the interior, all enhanced by beautiful flooring and fresh paint in select rooms completed within the past year. The private backyard is fully landscaped with lovely rose bushes that bloom in spring, lush trees, creating a tranquil oasis. Conveniently located near freeway access, ideal for commuters to Edwards Airforce base, and close to shopping. Explore the 3D tour and video for more details.No HOA , NO Mello-roos
